STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Faquan MARTIN, a/k/a Birth Al-Fuquan Martin, Alfuquan Martin, Fuquan J. Martin, Fuqua Martin and Devin M. Mays, Defendant-Petitioner. C-539 September Term 2018
081529 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 25, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000926-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
